snippet.title: Asterigos: Curse of the Stars - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Asterigos: Curse of the Stars is the upcoming Action RPG aiming to release in 2022 Q3 on the platforms of Steam, PlayStation, and Xbox.
